{"tid":1498183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以入黎比啲意見我，求下你地幫幫00後既我","createTime":"2019-08-23T09:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:27:07.000Z","uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a746d7227de2572189a1edd118b2a5ffd874e0c","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"借ac開post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係個好冇膽既年青人<br />\n呢個暑假一直都唔夠膽上最前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我想借住我係同陳同佳同一間學校既身份做反小小野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為雷射槍事件被人捉左既方師兄好似都係同一間<br />\n但係學校一直冇正面回應過呢啲事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好希望可以用連登既力量去感化呢間學校同埋入面既大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家大概既諗法就係係學校facebook page到開post再由咁多位巴絲轉發出去<br />\n相信陳同佳出反黎之後除左社會壓力之外可以比多一層壓力比佢!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請咁多位巴打比啲意見我同埋比啲支持我去做呢樣野<br />\n<strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申第一次開post，屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5daa45178ff19e95352437fdbee9165a1c43c258","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"細細力推"},{"pid":"f123e6beb7369a31b517a3afc3870a459b999e95","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"8c8cef161efc3c237f2f3122a14580dd66991aec","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"十連之第一推"},{"pid":"5bc0264381fd4e791a86f2e7996c3b1bdb9b1528","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"推二"},{"pid":"405ab6f94885fc19eca582b37c7ec5a8410f56eb","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:54:27.000Z","msg":"推三"},{"pid":"82e9c03ec72d8fcc8c4470d2170f8eb354d15ec8","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"推四"},{"pid":"0c4953c7ade61b04492e0bf53398f07639659adb","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"推五"},{"pid":"c651a43f1753cb32bda13cbec45c28e67d7b4b46","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"推六"},{"pid":"231ebf1e99923fe3856349f66f9fb7e61f8c3182","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"推七"},{"pid":"f12d3ed9ee9aa15c5d58cf617622e1427aadc72a","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"推八"},{"pid":"3bb60c71a20b973c412e563fdaefd65a5fd67d10","tid":1498183,"uid":302691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"推九"},{"pid":"88ecc0645789bccdc7861ea3d83af7957cb9489e","tid":1498183,"uid":30